Paranilothauma and Neelamia, New Genera of Chironomini (Diptera: Chiromidae) from BrazilTwo new genera of Chironomini, Paraniloihauma gen.nov. and Neelamia gen.nov. are erected. Paranilothauma reissi spec. nov. is described from adult males and pupae; Neelamia fittkaui spec.nov. and Neelamia bergeri spec.nov. are described from adult males. All species were collected in the Amazon Valley of Brazil.